<doc id="884497" wikidata="Q5971826" url="?curid=884497" title="Magnús Þór Hafsteinsson">
<text>Magnús Þór Hafsteinsson (born May 29, 1964) is an Icelandic politician active in the Liberal Party (Frjálslyndi flokkurinn).

He has also worked as a reporter for the public TV news and is educated as a biologist.

